data.description: Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to own an end unit in the picturesque Groves Park Commons neighborhood. This lovely community is characterized by its community park, tree-lined streets, and sidewalks. The 'Raleigh' floor plan features 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on the main floor and the third bedroom and bathroom upstairs. The kitchen is spacious and well-appointed, offering granite countertops, a stainless steel appliance package (including a gas stove), a tasteful tiled backsplash, and a convenient pantry. Hardwood floors grace the main living areas, dining room, and living room, adding to the elegance of the space.The main level owner's suite is a retreat in itself, complete with a generously-sized walk-in closet, a double bowl vanity, and a beautifully tiled walk-in shower. For your storage needs, the 2-car garage provides ample space, along with additional storage in the floored attic space. Enjoy the expansive community park in this tranquil setting, enveloped by the beauty of old-growth trees. The location is also incredibly convenient, with a wealth of shopping and dining options within a 2-mile radius and easy access to ORNL, Y-12, and West Knoxville, making this a truly desirable place to call home.
